snippet.title: DESTINATA RED 3.0 TRAILER
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1489160/Destinata_ROJO_COMPLETO/


Destinata is a pixel art platformer (in case the imagery didn't tell) with branches dividing the game in a dynamic and mysterious visual novel and a fast-paced platformer. (pretty fun, would buy)
